      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t再烂今年全球电影票房前10好莱坞独占8成，<mark>支那</mark>烂片离开支那基本无人问津🤣<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvM2ZhMmUyODc4YTkzZGQ3YjdmYmVjLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMTc5JmhlaWdodD0yMTUz\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3fa2e2878a93dd7b7fbec.jpg?width=1179&amp;height=2153\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3fa2e2878a93dd7b7fbec.jpg?width=1179&amp;height=2153\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3fa2e2878a93dd7b7fbec.jpg?width=1179&amp;height=2153\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
      "date": "2023-12-20",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "729107",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "马丽",
        "uid": "123119"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t好萊塢電影的繁榮始終離不開她以美國基石文化爲依托的多元化風格\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2024-02-19",
